<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Konstantinos Balla | Mobile Portfolio</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Mobile portfolio for Konstantinos Balla" />

    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #070b1a;
        --bg-soft: rgba(10, 16, 36, 0.86);
        --panel: rgba(16, 23, 48, 0.78);
        --panel-strong: rgba(18, 27, 56, 0.95);
        --text: #f5f7ff;
        --muted: #aab4d4;
        --cyan: #4de2ff;
        --pink: #ff4fd8;
        --purple: #8f7cff;
        --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
        --shadow: 0 22px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.34);
        --radius: 24px;
        --radius-sm: 18px;
        --page-pad: 18px;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      html {
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
      }

      body {
        min-height: 100vh;
        font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at 10% 0%, rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.2), transparent 30%),
          radial-gradient(circle at 90% 20%, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.2), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(rgba(7, 11, 26, 0.78), rgba(7, 11, 26, 0.9)),
          url("./backround.png") center / cover no-repeat fixed;
        line-height: 1.6;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      body.menu-open {
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      body::before,
      body::after {
        content: "";
        position: fixed;
        width: 260px;
        height: 260px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        filter: blur(90px);
        opacity: 0.25;
        z-index: -2;
        pointer-events: none;
        animation: floatGlow 10s ease-in-out infinite;
      }

      body::before {
        top: -80px;
        left: -110px;
        background: var(--cyan);
      }

      body::after {
        right: -100px;
        bottom: 10%;
        background: var(--pink);
        animation-delay: 2s;
      }

      a {
        color: inherit;
      }

      img {
        display: block;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .phone-shell {
        width: min(100%, 480px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--page-pad) 32px;
      }

      .section {
        padding: 42px 0 0;
      }

      .section-kicker {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        color: var(--cyan);
        font-size: 0.76rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .section-kicker::before {
        content: "";
        width: 28px;
        height: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), transparent);
      }

      .section-title {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        font-size: clamp(1.85rem, 8vw, 2.55rem);
        line-height: 1.08;
        letter-spacing: -0.04em;
      }

      .section-title span,
      .gradient-text {
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--pink));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
      }

      .section-copy {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.98rem;
      }

      .glass-card {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: var(--radius);
        background: var(--panel);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(16px);
      }

      .glass-card::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.08), transparent 42%, rgba(255, 79, 216, 0.08));
        pointer-events: none;
      }

      .navbar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 1000;
        padding: 12px 0;
        background: rgba(7, 11, 26, 0.66);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      }

      .nav-inner {
        width: min(100%, 480px);
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 var(--page-pad);
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .logo {
        width: 54px;
        height: 54px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border-radius: 50%;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        font-weight: 950;
        background:
          linear-gradient(var(--bg), var(--bg)) padding-box,
          linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--pink)) border-box;
        border: 3px solid transparent;
        box-shadow: 0 0 28px rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.22);
      }

      .menu-toggle {
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 16px;
        color: var(--text);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        cursor: pointer;
      }

      .menu-toggle span,
      .menu-toggle::before,
      .menu-toggle::after {
        content: "";
        display: block;
        width: 21px;
        height: 2px;
        margin: 3px 0;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: currentColor;
        transition: transform 0.25s ease, opacity 0.25s ease;
      }

      .menu-toggle.active::before {
        transform: translateY(8px) rotate(45deg);
      }

      .menu-toggle.active span {
        opacity: 0;
      }

      .menu-toggle.active::after {
        transform: translateY(-8px) rotate(-45deg);
      }

      .nav-links {
        position: fixed;
        top: 78px;
        left: 18px;
        right: 18px;
        max-width: 444px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        padding: 16px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(9, 14, 32, 0.96);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        transform: translateY(-10px) scale(0.98);
        transition: opacity 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
      }

      .nav-links.open {
        opacity: 1;
        pointer-events: auto;
        transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
      }

      .nav-links a {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 13px 14px;
        border-radius: 16px;
        color: var(--muted);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .nav-links a::after {
        content: "↗";
        color: var(--cyan);
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 32px 0 0;
      }

      .tag {
        width: fit-content;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        padding: 8px 13px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        color: var(--cyan);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        max-width: 390px;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        font-size: clamp(2.55rem, 11vw, 4.1rem);
        line-height: 0.98;
        letter-spacing: -0.06em;
      }

      .hero h1 span {
        display: inline-block;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--pink));
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
      }

      .intro {
        margin-bottom: 24px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 1rem;
      }

      .hero-buttons {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .button {
        min-height: 52px;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 8px;
        padding: 0 16px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.92rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        transition: transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
      }

      .button:active {
        transform: scale(0.98);
      }

      .button-primary {
        color: #07101f;
        background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--cyan), var(--pink));
        box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.18);
      }

      .button-secondary {
        color: var(--text);
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
      }

      .hero-socials {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }

      .hero-socials a {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 40px;
        padding: 0 13px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .hero-card {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .hero-photo {
        overflow: hidden;
        aspect-ratio: 1 / 1.12;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 22px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      }

      .hero-photo img {
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .photo-note {
        margin-top: 12px;
        padding: 13px 14px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
        border-radius: 16px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        display: grid;
        gap: 10px;
        margin-top: 14px;
      }

      .stat {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
        gap: 12px;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 13px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.09);
        border-radius: 17px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
      }

      .stat-icon {
        width: 38px;
        height: 38px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        border-radius: 13px;
        color: var(--cyan);
        background: rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.16);
      }

      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.2rem;
        line-height: 1.1;
      }

      .stat span {
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }

      .about-card {
        margin-top: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .about-list {
        position: relative;
        list-style: none;
        display: grid;
        gap: 13px;
      }

      .about-list li {
        display: flex;
        gap: 11px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .about-list li::before {
        content: "✓";
        width: 24px;
        height: 24px;
        display: grid;
        place-items: center;
        flex: 0 0 auto;
        border-radius: 50%;
        color: var(--cyan);
        background: rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.08);
        border: 1px solid rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.2);
        font-weight: 900;
      }

      .skill-pills {
        position: relative;
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 9px;
        margin-top: 18px;
      }

      .skill-pills span {
        padding: 8px 12px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 0.84rem;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .timeline {
        display: grid;
        gap: 14px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .timeline-item {
        position: relative;
        padding: 18px 18px 18px 48px;
      }

      .timeline-item::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 20px;
        top: 24px;
        width: 13px;
        height: 13px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--cyan), var(--pink));
        box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.5);
      }

      .timeline-item::after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 26px;
        top: 38px;
        bottom: -15px;
        width: 1px;
        background: linear-gradient(var(--cyan), transparent);
        opacity: 0.5;
      }

      .timeline-item:last-child::after {
        display: none;
      }

      .timeline-top {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .timeline-top h3 {
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 1.02rem;
        line-height: 1.25;
      }

      .timeline-date {
        color: var(--cyan);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
        font-weight: 900;
      }

      .timeline-company {
        margin-top: 8px;
        color: var(--pink);
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .timeline-text {
        margin-top: 6px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .project-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .project-card-link {
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .project-card {
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      .project-media {
        aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
        overflow: hidden;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
      }

      .project-media img {
        height: 100%;
        object-fit: cover;
      }

      .project-body {
        position: relative;
        padding: 18px;
      }

      .project-tag {
        display: inline-flex;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        padding: 7px 10px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        color: var(--cyan);
        background: rgba(77, 226, 255, 0.08);
        font-size: 0.72rem;
        font-weight: 900;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      .project-body h3 {
        margin-bottom: 8px;
        font-size: 1.15rem;
      }

      .project-body p {
        margin-bottom: 14px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.93rem;
      }

      .project-footer {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 12px;
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        font-weight: 800;
      }

      .project-footer span:last-child {
        color: var(--cyan);
      }

      .contact-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 16px;
        margin-top: 20px;
      }

      .contact-card,
      .cta-card {
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .contact-list {
        position: relative;
        list-style: none;
        display: grid;
        gap: 15px;
      }

      .contact-list li {
        display: grid;
        gap: 4px;
      }

      .contact-list strong {
        color: var(--text);
        font-size: 0.92rem;
      }

      .contact-list a {
        color: var(--muted);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.94rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
      }

      .cta-card h3 {
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-size: 1.35rem;
        line-height: 1.16;
      }

      .cta-card p {
        position: relative;
        margin-bottom: 18px;
        color: var(--muted);
        font-size: 0.95rem;
      }

      .cta-card .button {
        position: relative;
        width: 100%;
      }

      .footer {
        padding: 36px 0 20px;
        color: var(--muted);
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.82rem;
      }

      .to-top {
        position: fixed;
        right: 18px;
        bottom: 18px;
        z-index: 990;
        width: 48px;
        height: 48px;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.14);
        border-radius: 50%;
        color: var(--text);
        background: rgba(7, 11, 26, 0.76);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        cursor: pointer;
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        transform: translateY(10px);
        transition: opacity 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
      }

      .to-top.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        pointer-events: auto;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      .reveal {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(24px);
        transition: opacity 0.65s ease, transform 0.65s ease;
      }

      .reveal.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }

      @keyframes floatGlow {
        0%, 100% {
          transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
        }

        50% {
          transform: translateY(18px) scale(1.05);
        }
      }

      @media (min-width: 760px) {
        .phone-shell,
        .nav-inner {
          max-width: 740px;
        }

        .hero-buttons {
          max-width: 390px;
        }

        .hero-card {
          display: grid;
          grid-template-columns: 0.95fr 1fr;
          gap: 14px;
          align-items: start;
        }

        .project-grid {
          grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
        }

        .contact-grid {
          grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
      <div class="nav-inner">
        <a href="#home" class="logo" aria-label="KB home">KB</a>

        <button class="menu-toggle" id="menuToggle" aria-label="Toggle menu" aria-expanded="false">
          <span></span>
        </button>

        <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
          <a href="#about">About</a>
          <a href="#experience">Experience</a>
          <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
          <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </nav>

    <div class="phone-shell">
      <header class="hero" id="home">
        <div class="reveal">
          <p class="tag">Portfolio • Web Designer • Cybersecurity</p>

          <h1>Hello, I'm <span>Konstantinos Balla</span></h1>

          <p class="intro">
            I’m a cybersecurity professional focused on identifying vulnerabilities, securing web applications,
            and strengthening system defenses through practical, real-world security work.
          </p>

          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a href="#projects" class="button button-primary">View Projects →</a>
            <a href="#contact" class="button button-secondary">Contact Me</a>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-socials" aria-label="Social links">
            <a href="#">GitHub</a>
            <a href="#">LinkedIn</a>
            <a href="https://instagram.com/yourhandle" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Instagram</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="hero-card glass-card reveal" aria-label="Profile summary">
          <div>
            <div class="hero-photo">
              <img src="./photo1.png" alt="Konstantinos Balla portrait" />
            </div>
            <div class="photo-note">
              Always learning, always securing.
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-icon">🛡</div>
              <div>
                <strong>1+</strong>
                <span>Years in Cybersecurity</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-icon">⌘</div>
              <div>
                <strong>3+</strong>
                <span>Websites Built</span>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="stat">
              <div class="stat-icon">☏</div>
              <div>
                <strong>3+</strong>
                <span>Years in Customer Service</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </header>

      <main>
        <section id="about" class="section">
          <div class="section-kicker reveal">About</div>
          <h2 class="section-title reveal">Cybersecurity work with <span>real-world impact.</span></h2>
          <p class="section-copy reveal">
            I combine security knowledge, technical problem-solving, and a strong eye for clean digital experiences.
          </p>

          <div class="about-card glass-card reveal">
            <ul class="about-list">
              <li>I identify vulnerabilities and help improve system and application security.</li>
              <li>I build responsive websites that look polished on desktop, tablet, and mobile.</li>
              <li>I combine cybersecurity, frontend development, and usability into one strong digital experience.</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="skill-pills" aria-label="Skills">
              <span>SIEM</span>
              <span>EDR</span>
              <span>JavaScript</span>
              <span>UI Design</span>
              <span>Critical Thinking</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="experience" class="section">
          <div class="section-kicker reveal">Experience</div>
          <h2 class="section-title reveal">Selected roles and technical work.</h2>

          <div class="timeline">
            <article class="timeline-item glass-card reveal">
              <div class="timeline-top">
                <h3>Cybersecurity SOC Analyst</h3>
                <span class="timeline-date">2025–2026</span>
              </div>
              <p class="timeline-company">CBS-LAN</p>
              <p class="timeline-text">
                Monitored, detected, investigated, and responded to cybersecurity threats in real time.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="timeline-item glass-card reveal">
              <div class="timeline-top">
                <h3>Back Office Employee</h3>
                <span class="timeline-date">2025</span>
              </div>
              <p class="timeline-company">Mediatel</p>
              <p class="timeline-text">
                Worked on the migration of DEH from SAP to Salesforce.
              </p>
            </article>

            <article class="timeline-item glass-card reveal">
              <div class="timeline-top">
                <h3>Network Engineer</h3>
                <span class="timeline-date">2024–2025</span>
              </div>
              <p class="timeline-company">OPAP-ALLWIN</p>
              <p class="timeline-text">
                Helped keep company virtual machines, servers, and network infrastructure reliable.
              </p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section id="projects" class="section">
          <div class="section-kicker reveal">Projects</div>
          <h2 class="section-title reveal">Projects that reflect both design and security.</h2>
          <p class="section-copy reveal">
            Replace the sample links with your live project URLs when they are ready.
          </p>

          <div class="project-grid">
            <a href="https://your-nail-salon-website.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="project-card-link reveal">
              <article class="project-card glass-card">
                <div class="project-media">
                  <img src="./project1.png" alt="Preview of Nail Salon Website" />
                </div>
                <div class="project-body">
                  <span class="project-tag">Web Design</span>
                  <h3>Nail Salon Website</h3>
                  <p>A stylish beauty brand website with a premium feel and elegant visual presentation.</p>
                  <div class="project-footer">
                    <span>Brand / Web</span>
                    <span>Open ↗</span>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </article>
            </a>

